Email Engagement Filters

Here are some examples of common email engagement use cases.

Subject Line Engagement

This filter finds individuals who opened an email with the subject line of Holiday Special.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Open
AND
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Holiday Special

Opens by Subject Line and Purchases

This filter finds individuals who made a purchase and opened an email with the subject line of Holiday Flash Sale.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Holiday Flash Sale
AND
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Open

AND

Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 0

Opens by Subject Line and Total Purchase by Month

This filter looks for seasonal spenders who opened an email with the subject line of Holiday Flash Sale and made purchases greater than $1,000 in December.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Holiday Flash Sale
AND
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Open

AND

Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 1000
AND
Order Start Date | Month Of Year | December

Subject Line Engagement by Multiple Locations in the Last 7 Days

This filter finds individuals who had some engagement based in New York or San Francisco and opened an email with the subject line of Pop Up Store Surprise in the last 7 days.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Pop Up Store Surprise
AND
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Open
AND
Engagement Date Time | Last Number Of Days | 6
AND
City Name | Is In | New York, San Francisco

ALTERNATIVE EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Pop Up Store Surprise
AND
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Open
AND
Engagement Date Time | Last Number Of Days | 6
AND
City Name | Is In | New York

OR

Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Pop Up Store Surprise
AND
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Open
AND
Engagement Date Time | Last Number Of Days | 6
AND
City Name | Is In | San Francisco

Not Opened by Location in the Last 3 Months

This filter finds individuals who have not opened email in the last 3 months, and with an IP address identified as New York City.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | Exactly | 0
Engagement Channel Action | Is Not Equal To | Open

AND

City Name | Is Equal To | New York
AND
Engagement Date Time | Last Number Of Months | 2

Subject Line Engagement by Country

This filter finds individuals who engaged with the subject line of Early Black Friday Sale, have an engagement channel action of Open, and Country as the United States.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 1
Engagement Channel Action | Is Equal To | Open
AND
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Early Black Friday Sale
AND
Country | Is Equal To | United States

No Email Engagement

This filter looks for customers who have no email engagement.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | Exactly | 0
Subject Line Text | Is Equal To | Holiday Sales
